sentences: Gordana "Goca" Božinovska (Serbian Cyrillic: Гордана "Гоца" Божиновска; born 16 January 1965)
Born in the village of Samaila near Kraljevo, she started her career by performing in kafanas dodging Ibar Highway alongside Vesna Zmijanac.
In 2013, she was a contestant on the reality show Farma, finishing in fourth place.
Božinovska was married to kick-boxer and alleged leader of Surčin Clan, Zoran Šijan, who was assassinated in 1999 under unresolved circumstances.
